quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,84,kaho ke hum khuda par imaan laaye aur jo kitaab hum par nazil hui aur jo saheefay ibrahim aur ismael aur ashq aur Yaqoob aur un ki aulaad par utre aur jo kitaaben moose aur eesa aur dosray anbia ko perwar-digaar ki taraf se milein sab par imaan laaye hum un payghambaroon mein se kisi mein kuch farq nahi karte aur hum isi ( khuday-e wahid ) ke farmaa bardaar hain
  3,85,aur jo shakhs islam ke siwa kisi aur deen ka taalib hoga woh is se hargiz qubool nahikiya jaye ga aur aisa shakhs akhirat mein nuqsaan uthany walon mein hoga
  3,86,khuda aisay logon ko kyonkr hadaayat day jo imaan laane ke baad kafir hogaye aur ( pehlay ) is baat ki gawahi day chuke ke yeh paighambar brhq hai aur un ke paas dalail bhi aagaye aur khuda be insafon ko hadaayat nahi deta
  3,87,un logon ki saza yeh hai ke un par khuda ki aur firshton ki aur insanon ki sab ki laanat ho
  3,88,hamesha is laanat mein ( girftar ) rahen ge un se nah to azaab halkakiya jaye ga aur nah inhen mohlat day jaye gi
  3,89,haan jinhon ne is ke baad tauba ki aur apni haalat durust kar li to khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  3,90,jo log imaan laane ke baad kafir ho gay phir kufar mein barhatay gay aison ki tauba hargiz qubool nah hogi aur yeh log gumraah hain
  3,91,jo log kafir hue aur kufar hi ki haalat mein mar gay woh agar ( nijaat haasil karni chahain aur ) badlay mein zameen bhar kar sona den to hargiz qubool nahkiya jaye ga un logon ko dukh dainay wala azaab ho ga aur un ki koi madad nahi kere ga
